Sorry if this post contains a few typos. I nearly got my arm broken at 
Taekwuando, and its a bit painful to type. I'll try to fix any typos I make.

::Zardus/Bloodystrike::

Zardus looks from Feline to the kneeling Skulletron (he's still kneeling, 
right?).

"Yes, you two will be working together. But first of all," he says, studying 
Skulletron carefully, "The computers report that you have the power to tamper 
with the emotions of other bots, is that true?"

Zardus waits for Skulletron's answer, noticing Bloodystrike nodding in the 
background. If it was true, Skulletron would be able to complete his part of 
the mission. Zardus had no doubt in Feline's capability, now he just had to 
make sure of Skulletron's.
